<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q14_v1" title="Q14_v1" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceC</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>Una persona realiza el siguiente procedimiento para factorizar la suma 
      <m:math>
        <m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn>
      </m:math>, cometiendo un error.
    </p>
    <p>Paso 1: escribe cada sumando como el producto de dos números con un mismo factor, obteniendo 
      <m:math>
        <m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn>
      </m:math>.
    </p>
    <p>Paso 2: descompone cada factor en números primos, obteniendo 
      <m:math>
        <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn>
      </m:math>.
    </p>
    <p>Paso 3: escribe las potencias correspondientes, obteniendo 
      <m:math>
        <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn>
      </m:math>.
    </p>
    <p>Paso 4: factoriza la suma, obteniendo 
      <m:math>
        <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
      </m:math>.
      ¿Cuál es el último paso en el que la igualdad sigue siendo verdadera?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">El Paso 1<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. En el Paso 1 sí se mantiene la igualdad, porque 6·3 + 6·5 = 18 + 30. Pero también en el Paso 2 se mantiene, ya que 2·3·3 + 2·3·5 = 18 + 30. Por lo tanto, el último paso verdadero no es el Paso 1.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">El Paso 2<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. En el Paso 2 se mantiene la igualdad, pero en el Paso 3 también, porque 2·3² + 2·3·5 = 2·9 + 30 = 18 + 30 = 48. Por lo tanto, el último paso verdadero no es el Paso 2.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">El Paso 3<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Hasta el Paso 3 la igualdad sigue siendo verdadera: 2·3² + 2·3·5 = 2·9 + 2·15 = 18 + 30 = 48. En cambio, el Paso 4 da 2·3²(1 + 5) = 18·6 = 108, y 108 ≠ 48. Por eso, el último paso verdadero es el Paso 3.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">El Paso 4<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El Paso 4 no mantiene la igualdad, porque 2·3² + 2·3·5 = 18 + 30 = 48, mientras que 2·3²(1 + 5) = 18·6 = 108. Como 108 ≠ 48, el Paso 4 es falso.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Verificar la igualdad inicial</strong></p>
            <p>La suma original es:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn>
            </m:math>
            <p>En el Paso 1 se escribe:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn>
            </m:math>
            <p>Calculamos cada producto:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn>
            </m:math>
            <p>y</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn>
            </m:math>
            <p>Entonces, el Paso 1 sí es correcto.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Revisar la descomposición en factores primos</strong></p>
            <p>Se obtiene:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn>
            </m:math>
            <p>Calculamos cada término:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn>
            </m:math>
            <p>y</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn>
            </m:math>
            <p>Entonces, el Paso 2 también es correcto.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Revisar el uso de potencias</strong></p>
            <p>Se escribe:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn>
            </m:math>
            <p>Como</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn>
            </m:math>
            <p>se tiene:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn>
            </m:math>
            <p>y además:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn>
            </m:math>
            <p>Entonces, el Paso 3 también mantiene la igualdad.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Comprobar la factorización propuesta</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión del Paso 3 es:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn>
            </m:math>
            <p>Su valor es:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>48</m:mn>
            </m:math>
            <p>En el Paso 4 se propone:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
            </m:math>
            <p>Calculamos:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn>
            </m:math>
            <p>y luego:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>108</m:mn>
            </m:math>
            <p>Como</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mn>108</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>48</m:mn>
            </m:math>
            <p>el Paso 4 es incorrecto.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El último paso en que la igualdad sigue siendo verdadera es el <strong>Paso 3</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>